ğŸš€ What You Get:

**Documented APIs:**

**Authentication:**
- `POST /api/auth/login` - User authentication
- `POST /api/auth/signup` - User registration
- `POST /api/auth/logout` - User logout

**User Management:**
- `GET /api/auth/me` - Get current user information
- `GET /api/auth/session` - Get session status and user information

**Profile Management:**
- `GET /api/profile` - Get comprehensive user profile data
- `PUT /api/profile` - Update user profile data
- `PUT /api/auth/updateProfile` - Update profile (legacy endpoint)

**Draft Management:**
- `GET /api/auth/drafts` - Get user's drafts
- `POST /api/auth/createDrafts` - Create new draft
- `PUT /api/auth/updateDraft` - Update existing draft
- `DELETE /api/auth/deletedrafts` - Delete draft

